         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head>
            <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en"><p><note>1.i</note>: Bellerophon; <note>ii</note>: Chimera</p>
            <p><note>2.i</note>: Hector; <note>ii</note>: Achilles; <note>iii</note>: Xanthos, Balios</p>
            <p><note>3.i</note>: Sirens; <note>ii</note>: Approach and listen, Odysseus. This is the sound of the loud sirens; who, having heard the song has sailed 
               past the meadow?</p>
            <p><note>4</note>: Scylla;</p>
            <p><note>1.i</note>: Pyrrhus; <note>ii</note>: Polyxena</p></div>
            
