         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>2.iii: The horses of Achilles, <title>Iliad</title> 16.149, 19.400</p>
            <p>3.ii: A close reference to Homer, ἠδ’ ὡς Σειρήνων ἁδινάων φθόγγον ἄκουσεν, <title>Odyssey</title> 23.326. For the meadow of the Sirens see Odyssey 12.43</p>
         </div>
         
